::Spears::

She hit her fist against the wall again with a loud 'Bang'.  She 
heard Striker outside her room. She stopped and took a deep breath.
"Yeah, I'm in here. Whatcha want?" She walked to the door and opened 
it.  Her hand was bruised, but OK.  She looked at him with anger in 
her eyes. "Yeah?"
